<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-05 01:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5356 &Cx1f; taf-z
r a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NATIONAL-SLUGLIST-CLO     06-05 2259
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-NATIONAL-SLUGLIST-CLOSER </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
