<SLUG> BC-EXTRA-NEW-FACE-ON-ENDANGERED-SPECIES-ACT-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE ENDANGERED SPECIES ACT GETS A MAKEOVER 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;    (This is one of nine special ``one-shot'' features culled from
