<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-05 11:32 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5650 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-LYNCH-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      06-05 0667
