and Tyche Hendricks. Moved 6-4.
</P>
<P>
   DUELINGEVANGELISTS-TEX (Undated) _ Consider it a theological
shootout between two of the country's most avidly evangelical
faiths. This weekend, thousands of Southern Baptists armed with
books and videos challenging Mormon beliefs will sweep into Salt
Lake City to combine their annual convention with a door-to-door
blitz seeking to convert Mormons. The Mormons, secure in their own
religious heartland, plan to welcome the Baptists. By Jim Jones.
Moved 6-3.
</P>
