resigned Tuesday as spiritual leader of the Palm Beach Catholic
diocese, admitting he sexually molested five boys early in his long
career as a priest. His stunning confession brought a crisis of
faith that reaches from here to the Vatican. By Dan Moffett. Moved
6-2.
