<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LONGHORNS-LOSETRACK06-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    NCAA outdoor championship: Texas high jumpers come crashing down
 &HT;    By Randy Riggs
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
