<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-05 18:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6501 &Cx1f; tad-z
r s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MARLINS-KOTSAY06-COX     06-05 0523
