<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-05 21:51 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6969 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-WARSH-COLUMN-BOS &LR;      06-05 1315
